      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以底层存储是FinTech_AuthVault？我需要确认这个组件的定位——它是专门存敏感认证资料的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，AuthVault是隔离的存储层。整个流程从FinTech_LedgerService开始初始化，它要负责加载后端适配。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Init"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把LedgerService画成入口节点，标注Init状态。它需要require backend到另一个LedgerService实例吗？",
